data.description: Sweet Carolina Living! Dorchester District Two Schools! This gorgeous home is located on a stunning over-sized lot in desirable Highwoods Plantation of Summerville. As you enter through the front porch you are greeted with new flooring, fresh paint, and much more! The kitchen features a breakfast bar, pantry, large dining area with chair rail molding and access to the backyard and two car finished garage. Cozy up in the spacious family room by the wood burning fireplace, perfect for sipping your fall pumpkin spice latte. Upstairs is sure to wow with brand new carpet, a loft, full guest bathroom, laundry room and two secondary bedrooms including walk-in closets. The main suite features tray ceiling, backyard view and ensuite with dual vanity, relaxing garden tub and large walk-in closet.Enjoy entertaining outback in your private oasis on your massive pie shaped lot with patio, shady trees and custom privacy fence, this space is a true zen paradise. More Features include a new HVAC system installed in 2021 with new smart thermostat and transferable warranty, fresh interior paint, new custom front yard mailbox and post, fresh landscape with crepe myrtle trees, oak, new white rock, stone curbing and much more! Please see Property Improvements, Highlights and Features Sheet for more details in Photos. Highwoods Plantation is just a few miles from Historic Downtown Summerville, and right around the corner from great shopping, entertainment, and nightlife options. Don't miss out on this perfect home located where natural beauty can be found, only 30 minutes to Charleston International Airport and only 44 minutes to downtown Charleston, South Carolina. Please schedule your private tour today!
